      "Number of Applicable L4 Business Processes": "This field displays the total number of applicable Level 4 Business Processes for the specified Group Company and Business Domain.",
      "Number of L4 Business Processes in Draft State": "This field displays the total number of level 4 Business Processes in 'Draft' State for the specified Group Company and Business Domain.",
