      "Number of Processes with Target Automation update (Since date Selected)": "This field displays the total number of unique Business Processes that have had either their Target Recommendation Remark/Explination or Target automation level updated for the selected Group Company and Business Domain since the selected filter date.\n\nNote: If the same Business Process Remark was updated multiple times after the filter date, it is counted only once.",
